Query_Description: Simple projection: SELECT l_orderkey l_shipdate FROM lineitem LIMIT 1000
Filter & projection: SELECT * FROM orders WHERE o_orderstatus = 'F'
Aggregation: SELECT o_custkey COUNT(*) FROM orders GROUP BY o_custkey
Aggregation & sorting: SELECT o_orderpriority COUNT(*) AS cnt FROM orders GROUP BY o_orderpriority ORDER BY cnt DESC
Join & aggregation: SELECT c_nationkey SUM(l_extendedprice) FROM customer JOIN orders JOIN lineitem GROUP BY c_nationkey
